{"word":"ἰύζω","slug":"ἰύζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰύζω</b></el> <el>(ἰύζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἰού'><el>ἰού</el></a>\n<p/><i>to shout, yell</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—later <i>to yell</i> or <i>cry</i> from grief or pain, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ῑ</el>, epic and <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>; <el>ῐ</el> in <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>\n"}]}